Program: Last Word
Title: 08/05/2009
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00k4l28
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 10 May 2009
Matthew Bannister talks to Nicky Weller and Steve White about the life of music manager John Weller; Adrian Jackson on Brazilian theatre director Augusto Boal; Arif Waqar on Ghazal singer Iqbal Bano; Anne Cole and Adrian Midgely on English toponymist Dr Margaret Gelling; Marianne Faithfull and Nicky Haslam on model and muse Maxime de la Falaise. Show less